♫ <i>Don't know where to go</i> ♫

405
00:25:08,400 --> 00:25:11,600
♫ <i>In the air, my memories flow</i> ♫

406
00:25:11,600 --> 00:25:14,200
♫ <i>Faces in a row</i> ♫

407
00:25:14,200 --> 00:25:17,800
♫ <i>Take a long way home</i> ♫

408
00:25:17,800 --> 00:25:24,700
♫ <i>But all of this reminds me to believe</i> ♫

409
00:25:24,700 --> 00:25:28,400
♫ <i>No one stays or leaves</i> ♫

410
00:25:28,400 --> 00:25:35,600
♫ <i>And all of this reminds me to receive</i> ♫

411
00:25:35,600 --> 00:25:39,000
♫ <i>The life we can see</i> ♫

